mso-pagination:widow-orphan;vertical-align:baseline"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: black; font-size: large;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 一、办公室人员：端午节放假<span lang="EN-US">3</span>天，即<span lang="EN-US">2018</span>年<span lang="EN-US">6</span>月<span lang="EN-US">16</span>日（星期六）至<span lang="EN-US">2018</span>年<span lang="EN-US">6</span>月<span lang="EN-US">18</span>日（星期一）</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: large; text-indent: 24pt;">放假，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: large; text-indent: 24pt;">6</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: large; text-indent: 24pt;">月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: large; text-indent: 24pt;">19</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: large; text-indent: 24pt;">日（星期二）正常上班。</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;
mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:28.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;vertical-align:baseline"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: black; font-size: large;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 二、项目部及传诚客栈人员：端午节放假<span lang="EN-US">1</span>天，即<span lang="EN-US">2018</span>年<span lang="EN-US">6</span>月<span lang="EN-US">18</span>日（星期一）放假，具体根据</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: large; text-indent: 24pt;">各项目部，传诚客栈安排。</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;
mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:28.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;
